# Product Sync Architecture

## Core Strategy

The [ProductSyncStrategy](mdc:strategies/ProductSyncStrategy.js) orchestrates product syncing between Shopify stores. It delegates specialized tasks to utility classes:

## Utility Classes

- **[ProductBatchProcessor](mdc:utils/ProductBatchProcessor.js)**: Handles fetching products in batches with pagination
- **[ProductOperationHandler](mdc:utils/ProductOperationHandler.js)**: Manages product creation and updating
- **[ProductMetafieldProcessor](mdc:utils/ProductMetafieldProcessor.js)**: Processes and syncs product metafields
- **[MetafieldFilterUtils](mdc:utils/MetafieldFilterUtils.js)**: Filters metafields by namespace and key
- **[SyncResultTracker](mdc:utils/SyncResultTracker.js)**: Tracks operation results and formats reports
